  "title": "<div>  •  Reinforces the idea that literature is about perception &amp hidden me",
  "content": "<div>  •  Reinforces the idea that literature is about perception &amp hidden meanings.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> 4. The XP System Overhaul – Absorption vs. Currency</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> XP is now split into two functions:</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Absorption – XP is permanently banked and used to evolve into the next power level.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Currency – XP is spent like coins to summon items, perform skill checks, or trade.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Example: XP Decision Point</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Action</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Effect</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Type of XP Usage</div>",
